---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pagination:
  data: catalog.sectors
  size: 1
  alias: sector
  addAllPagesToCollections: true
permalink: "/sectors/{{ sector.slug }}/"
eleventyComputed:
  title: "{{ sector.name | safe }} · The Sectors"
  description: "{{ sector.id }} {{ sector.name }}: what the sector includes, where AI and robotics could reduce costs, the guardrails, and the honest evidence status."
---
{% from "partials/content-needed.njk" import block as gap, inline as gapInline %}
{% set sc = sectorContent[sector.slug] %}
<section class="sector-head">
  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Uncost</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <a href="/sectors/">Sectors</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <span>{{ sector.name }}</span></div>
  <div class="sector-head-grid">
    <div>
      <h1 class="sector-title">{{ sector.name }}.</h1>
      <p class="sector-sub">{% if sector.includes %}{{ sector.includes }}{% else %}{{ gapInline("sector-includes") }}{% endif %}</p>
      <div class="sector-num">Sector <b>{{ sector.num }} / 15</b> · <span class="status status--{{ sector.statusClass }}">{{ sector.status }}</span> · Dossier <b>{{ sector.id }}</b></div>
    </div>
    <div>{% image sector.illustration.src, sector.illustration.alt, "(max-width: 920px) 280px, 620px", [280, 620, 1024] %}</div>
  </div>
</section>

<nav class="anchor-bar" aria-label="Page sections">
  <a href="#scope">Scope &amp; opportunity <span class="cnt">01</span></a>
  <a href="#evidence">Evidence status <span class="cnt">02</span></a>
  <a href="#worked">Worked example <span class="cnt">03</span></a>
  <a href="#projects">Related projects <span class="cnt">04</span></a>
  <a href="#sources">Sources <span class="cnt">05</span></a>
</nav>

<section id="scope" class="sblock sblock--ink sblock--flush">
  <div class="eyebrow">01 · Scope, opportunity, guardrail</div>
  <h2>Where automation could bite — and what stays visible.</h2>
  <div class="scope">
    <div><h3><i></i>What it includes</h3><p>{% if sector.includes %}{{ sector.includes }}{% else %}{{ gapInline("sector-includes") }}{% endif %}</p></div>
    <div><h3><i></i>The opportunity</h3><p>{% if sector.opportunity %}{{ sector.opportunity }}{% else %}{{ gapInline("sector-opportunity") }}{% endif %}</p></div>
    <div><h3><i></i>The guardrail</h3><p>{% if sector.guardrail %}{{ sector.guardrail }}{% else %}{{ gapInline("sector-guardrail") }}{% endif %}</p></div>
  </div>
  <p class="rmstatus">Roadmap status: <b>{{ sector.status }}</b>. Status is sequencing, not importance.</p>
</section>

<section id="evidence" class="sblock sblock--ink">
  <div class="eyebrow">02 · Evidence status</div>
  <h2>No number ships without a <span class="hl-coral">receipt</span>.</h2>
  <div class="evd-empty">
    {% if sector.evidence %}<h3>{{ sector.evidence }}</h3>{% else %}{{ gap("sector-evidence") }}{% endif %}
    <p>When {{ sector.name }} figures publish, each line carries: value, unit, region, date observed, a source ID from the public register, a confidence label, and the collection method.</p>
    <div class="chips">
      <span class="rcpt-conf rcpt-conf--confirmed">Confirmed</span>
      <span class="rcpt-conf rcpt-conf--estimate">Estimate</span>
      <span class="rcpt-conf rcpt-conf--scenario">Scenario</span>
      <span class="rcpt-conf rcpt-conf--needs-refresh">Needs refresh</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="worked" class="sblock">
  <div class="eyebrow">03 · How a {{ sector.name | lower }} cost gets uncosted</div>
  {% if sc.workedExample %}
  <h2>{{ sc.workedExample.scenario }}</h2>
  <p class="wx-lede">Nothing below is a finding. It is what the work would look like, step by step.</p>
  <div class="steps6">
    {%- for step in sc.workedExample.steps %}
    <div class="step6"><div class="n">{{ loop.index }}</div><p>{{ step }}</p></div>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <h2>The worked example.</h2>
  {{ gap("sector-worked-example", "research-gated sector — its dossier guardrail forbids patient-facing, child-facing, or enforcement work without qualified governance, so a 'a community group can run it' worked example would imply a service that does not exist. Only cost measurement is in scope today; author a measurement-only version with the founder, or keep gapped.") }}
  {% endif %}
</section>

{% if sector.guardrail %}
<section class="callout">
  <blockquote>&ldquo;{{ sector.guardrail }}&rdquo;</blockquote>
  <div class="attr">— The {{ sector.name }} guardrail · dossier {{ sector.id }}</div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section id="projects" class="sblock sblock--cream2 sblock--flush">
  <div class="eyebrow">04 · Related projects</div>
  <h2>Where {{ sector.name }} shows up in The Projects.</h2>
  {% if sector.relatedProjects.length %}
  <table class="prj-table">
    <thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>Project</th><th>Role</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
    {%- for p in sector.relatedProjects %}
      <tr>
        <td class="id">{{ p.id }}</td>
        <td class="title"><a href="/projects/{{ p.slug }}/">{{ p.display }}</a><span class="sum">{{ p.line }}</span></td>
        <td class="role">{% if p.layer %}{{ p.layer }}{% else %}{{ p.tag | capitalize }}{% endif %}</td>
        <td><span class="status status--planned">Draft</span></td>
      </tr>
    {%- endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
  {% else %}
  <p class="sec-lead">No project currently names {{ sector.name }} in its dossier. Projects appear here only when their own brief lists this sector.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>

<section id="sources" class="sblock">
  <div class="eyebrow">05 · Sources</div>
  <h2>The register comes before the figures.</h2>
  <p class="sec-lead">No sector-specific sources are registered for {{ sector.name }} yet. When they are, each record will carry a public ID, publisher, date, licence, refresh cadence and region coverage — and every figure on this page will cite one.</p>
  <p class="src-note">Official statistics first. Licences recorded at intake.</p>
  <p><a href="https://github.com/uncost-org/uncost/blob/main/sources/register.csv" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Browse the public register</a> · <a href="https://github.com/uncost-org/uncost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Propose a source</a></p>
</section>

<section class="sblock sblock--cream2">
  <div class="eyebrow">Related sectors</div>
  <h2>Keep reading.</h2>
  <div class="related">
    <a href="/sectors/"><span class="sq"></span> All 15 sectors →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sblock sblock--ink">
  <h2 class="cta-h">Help build the {{ sector.name | lower }} evidence. Sources before slogans.</h2>
  <p class="lead">Useful now: {{ sc.ctaRoles | join(", ") }}. As the work grows, a volunteer {{ sector.name }} lead.</p>
  <div class="cta-actions">
    <a href="/join" class="u-btn u-btn--primary">Take part</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/uncost-org/uncost" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="u-btn u-btn--outline-cream">The public records</a>
  </div>
</section>
